FERRARI TAKES 2 PARKING LOTS AT WATERWAY POINT ON SAT EVENING Submitted by farhan on Mon, 06/02/2017 - 11:20am 
On a Saturday evening (Feb 4) at 5 pm, a Ferrari driver decided that he should park his car in 2 parking lots at Waterway Point. 
So in case u missed it, this is #parkingcibai SLK8281C. Editor's Note:
